data.title: sp.blake_2511
data.meta_description:
Portland Trail Blazer guard Steve Blake visits with his wife Kristen and son Nicholas, 16 mos., from his hotel room in Indianapolis, IN. Blake used time between shoot around and the game to catch up with his family back home.
	
	photos by Bruce Ely
